<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Adult Incontinence products</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Persona Hygiene Wipes</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Toilet Paper</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Deodorant (for men &amp; women)</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Gift Card to store that sell these items.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Cash donations</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">Ways you can help:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Drive up and Drop donations at Central Church on April 22</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Drop off items at the church office (Mon-Fri 9am-3pm) before April 21</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Order items online to be delivered to Central Congregational Church</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">All items collected go towards Community Service of Newburyport, Inc. </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">Making It Persona</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: italic;">l</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;"> program. For more information contact Pamela Brown at </span><a href="mailto:wheaten1031@gmail.com" target="_blank" style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; font-style: normal;">wheaten1031@gmail.com</a><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">. </span></p>
